15 (i) The adoption of a resolution by the board of
16 county commissioners proposing to rescind the mill levy; or
17
18 (ii) The board of county commissioners receives
19 a petition to rescind the mill levy signed by qualified
20 electors resident in the district equal in number to not
21 less than fifteen percent (15%) of the voters resident in
22 the district who voted in the last general election. The
